Package tv.ux1.dao Description

The Data Access Object package

This package contains all of the classes for accessing the datastore. ux1.tv uses the objectify interface to the AppEngine datastore.

The DAO Objects will contain standard getXXX, putXXX, and deleteXXX methods, as well as higher level abstractions such as subscribe(), which may perform more than one atomic operation.
